id: stand_ground
title: "Standing Firm"

dialogue:
  - narrator: "You stand your ground firmly."
  - narrator: "The shadows circle around you but don't attack."
  - narrator: "It seems the forest respects courage."
  - narrator: "The shadows part, revealing a clear path."
  - narrator: "You walk calmly through the forest and find the exit."

next: ending_courage
